Package: spacelaser
Title: Cloud-Optimized Partial Reading of GEDI and ICESat-2 HDF5 Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Belian Earth", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "dev@belian.earth")
Description: Read GEDI and ICESat-2 satellite lidar data directly from NASA
    Earthdata cloud storage using HTTP range requests. Only fetches the bytes
    needed for the requested spatial subset, avoiding multi-gigabyte file
    downloads. Powered by a pure-Rust h5coro-style HDF5 partial reader.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.3.1
